For creating a repository go to Repositories then click the 'New' button in name section add any related name,then choose between public and private(if you want that anyone can see this my new repositories then choose public or if you want to make it hidden from anyone elese then set it as private) and then click on create readme file(it is optional but it is useful when we need to write any explanation of our pushed data,then we can write its explanation in htis readme file) and then at last click button 'create repository'.A repository will be created of given in repositories section.
//Commit keyword refers to change.Whenever we add or remove any data from our filr even a single dot,then to save it we have to commit it, commit means like a stamp of authenticity which says that save these changes.